 <h1 class="text-5xl font-extrabold text-white mt-4 mb-6 leading-tight">Magoosh TOEFL Review: The Best Way to Study on a Budget?</h1>
 <p class="text-xl text-neutral-400 leading-relaxed">Magoosh has long been a favorite for students who want a high-quality TOEFL prep course without spending hundreds of dollars. But is it still competitive in 2026? We spent 30 days testing the platform to see if it actually delivers on its promises.</p>
 </div>

