 <p class="font-bold text-white mb-4">Verdict</p>
 <p class="mb-0 leading-relaxed">Magoosh remains the best overall value in the TOEFL prep market. While it lacks the intensive human feedback of some premium courses, its video lessons and practice dashboard are world-class. If you are disciplined and want to save money, Magoosh is an easy recommendation.</p>
 </div>
