 <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mt-16 mb-6">What is Magoosh TOEFL?</h2>
 <p class="mb-6 leading-relaxed">Magoosh is a 100% online test prep company. Their TOEFL course is designed to be accessible on any device, making it perfect for busy students. Unlike traditional courses that rely on heavy textbooks, Magoosh focuses on short, digestible video lessons and a massive bank of practice questions.</p>
 <p class="mb-6 leading-relaxed">The platform is built around a "smart" dashboard that tracks your performance. It tells you your estimated score, identifies your weakest sections, and suggests which lessons you should watch next. This data-driven approach takes the guesswork out of studying.</p>

 <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mt-16 mb-6">Key Features</h2>
 
 <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-10 mb-4">1. High-Quality Video Lessons</h3>
 <p class="mb-6 leading-relaxed">Magoosh offers over 150 video lessons. They cover everything from basic grammar to advanced strategies for the Reading and Listening sections. The instructors are clear, engaging, and focus on the specific logic used by the TOEFL examiners. Each video is short (usually 5 to 10 minutes), which makes it easy to study even if you only have a small amount of time.</p>

 <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-10 mb-4">2. Realistic Practice Questions</h3>
 <p class="mb-6 leading-relaxed">With over 420 practice questions, Magoosh gives you plenty of opportunities to test your skills. The questions are very similar in difficulty and style to the real exam. The best part is that every single question has a detailed video explanation. If you get an answer wrong, you can immediately watch a tutor explain why the correct answer is right and why the others are wrong.</p>

 <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-10 mb-4">3. Score Predictor and Guarantee</h3>
 <p class="mb-6 leading-relaxed">As you answer practice questions, Magoosh uses an algorithm to predict your real TOEFL score. We found this predictor to be surprisingly accurate. Furthermore, Magoosh offers a 4-point score guarantee. If you have previously taken the TOEFL and your score does not improve by at least 4 points after using Magoosh, they will give you a full refund.</p>

