 <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mt-16 mb-6">Magoosh vs The Competition</h2>
 <p class="mb-6 leading-relaxed">Compared to <strong>Kaplan</strong>, Magoosh is much more affordable but offers fewer live resources. Compared to <strong>BestMyTest</strong>, Magoosh has better video lessons, but BestMyTest offers more practice tests and AI-powered feedback on speaking. If you want a balance of quality and price, Magoosh usually wins.</p>

 <div class="bg-blue-900/20 border border-blue-500/30 rounded-2xl p-8 my-12">
 <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Want Human Feedback?</h3>
