 <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Final Verdict</h2>
 <p class="text-blue-100 text-lg mb-8">Magoosh is the perfect choice for self-motivated students who want a structured, high-quality prep course without breaking the bank. It is the most reliable budget option on the market today.</p>
